channel.title: How Do I Make Commands?
channel.description:
[sup][b]Commands[/b]
Hello! I really need to know how to make commands... people say that there are command generators but i dont know what that is. can some one tell me how or send me a command generator. and how do i make the command for Mods+?
While u r here.. i just want to know how to make an item a 1hit kill.
Thank You! Kidd619[/sup] :)

item.title: How Do I Make Commands?
item.dc:creator: @pk3r_john pk3r john
item.description:
@pk3r_john wrote:

Try looking for other commands in your client.java, then just C&P them onto another line and you can change stuff.
